data.name: lblLibraryMaintenanceResetDatabase.Text
data.value: Delete all data from the database and rescan library folders. This will remove all tag mappings and custom metadata!

data.name: lblLibraryMaintenanceResetDeleted.Text
data.value: Remove deleted database entries. Note: If the images still exist, they will be added to the database when the next folder scan takes place.

data.name: lblViewingZoomLevelsHelp.Text
data.value:
Enter zoom levels in percentages separated by commas.
For example: "25,50,100,200" would set the available zoom levels to 25%, 50%, 100%, and 200%.
